flowchart LR
  W[Worker Laptop] -->|1. advertise readiness| T[Wi-Fi / LAN Transport]
  W -->|2. discover master| T
  W -->|3. worker_join_request| T

  T -->|4. discovery / packet ingress| M[Master Laptop]
  M -->|5. see candidate or join packet| M
  M -->|6. trust / pair / promote| M
  M -->|7. assignment_packet| T

  T -->|8. assignment_packet| W
  W -->|9. heartbeat packets| T
  W -->|10. worker_result / completion| T
  T -->|11. completion acknowledgement| M

  G[multi_ai_governance] -. decides policy / trust / approval / review .-> M
  G -. does not execute work .-> W
